tag-discussiontools-edit:
Short description of the discussiontools-edit tag.

Shown on lists of changes (history, recentchanges, etc.) for each edit to an existing comment made using DiscussionTools.

This message is always shown directly after {{msg-mw|tag-discussiontools}} and a comma.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|Tag-discussiontools-edit-description}}
